OL,3,CPeston: Why Rachel Reeves is likely to
OL,4,Cput up income tax
OL,6,FThere was a big moment at Prime
OL,7,FMinister's Questions when Keir Starmer
OL,8,Frefused to say he would stand by
OL,9,FLabour's manifesto promise not to
OL,10,Fincrease income tax, national
OL,11,Finsurance, or VAT.
OL,13,FThis is a telling contrast with what
OL,14,Fhe told MPs in July, when he
OL,15,Funambiguously stood by the manifesto's
OL,16,Ftax promises.
