OL,3,CPeston: Why Rachel Reeves is likely to
OL,4,Cput up income tax
OL,6,FEven before today, it was becoming
OL,7,Fincreasingly clear to me that the
OL,8,Fbudget would include a significant
OL,9,Frise in income tax - because it is the
OL,10,Fonly clean way, ministers tell me, to
OL,11,Ffill the #35 billion budget black hole.
OL,13,FStarmer seemed to me today to reveal
OL,14,Fhe believes an increase in income tax
OL,15,Fis inevitable.
OL,17,FI am less clear that the Chancellor is
OL,18,Fyet at that settled position, possibly
OL,19,Fbecause she is not sure she can
OL,20,Fsurvive the political thunderclap.
