OL,3,CPeston: Why Rachel Reeves is likely to
OL,4,Cput up income tax
OL,6,FIf Rachel Reeves were to increase the
OL,7,Fbasic rate of income tax on 26
OL,8,FNovember, it would be the first rise
OL,9,Fin the basic rate since 1975, when
OL,10,FHarold Wilson raised it to 35%.
OL,12,FSuccessive Tory and Labour governments
OL,13,Fhave subsequently cut it to the 20%
OL,14,Frate of today.
OL,16,FSo it would be wrong to downplay the
OL,17,Fpolitical and economic significance of
OL,18,Fthis moment.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
