OL,3,CPeston: Why Rachel Reeves is likely to
OL,4,Cput up income tax
OL,6,FAnd, by the way, only increasing the
OL,7,Fbasic rate raises significant sums
OL,8,Faccording to the government's own sums.
OL,10,FA 1p increase in the basic rate would
OL,11,Fraise #8.2bn, 1p on the 40p rate
OL,12,Fgarners #2.1bn and 1p on the 45p rate
OL,13,Fjust #230 million.
OL,15,FIf there were a 2p increase on all the
OL,16,Frates that would potentially raise #20
OL,17,Fbillion - which would be a meaningful
OL,18,Fcontribution to filling the estimated
OL,19,F#35 billion budget hole she needs to
OL,20,Ffill.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
