OL,3,CPeston: Why Rachel Reeves is likely to
OL,4,Cput up income tax
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FThe argument for putting up income
OL,12,Ftax, which I hear from many government
OL,13,Fmembers, is that attempting to raise
OL,14,F#35 billion from many different tax
OL,15,Fchanges would be messy, uncertain,
OL,16,Feconomically damaging and politically
OL,17,Frisky (think about the harm to Labour
OL,18,Fcaused by Reeves trying to raise a
OL,19,Fpaltry #500m from changes to farm and
OL,20,Fbusiness property inheritance tax
OL,21,Frelief).
