OL,3,CPeston: Why Rachel Reeves is likely to
OL,4,Cput up income tax
OL,6,FThe counter argument is that voters
OL,7,Fwon't forgive what they will see as
OL,8,Fthe lie perpetrated in Labour's
OL,9,Fmanifesto.
OL,11,FMy judgement is we will see a rise in
OL,12,Fincome tax, because the alternatives
OL,13,Fare worse. But I understand why this
OL,14,Fis causing anxiety and consternation
OL,15,Fat the top of government.
